<div class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Warranty Information</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg">Details about our warranty coverage for all jewelry purchased from Ottawa Opal Shop.</p>
</div>

<div class="space-y-8">
    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Standard Warranty</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">All jewelry purchased from Ottawa Opal Shop comes with a one-year limited warranty against manufacturing defects. This warranty covers issues related to craftsmanship and materials under normal wear.</p>

        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">What's Covered:</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-1">
            <li>Manufacturing defects in materials and workmanship</li>
            <li>Loose gemstones due to defective settings</li>
            <li>Broken clasps or closures (when not caused by misuse)</li>
            <li>Tarnishing beyond normal expectations</li>
            <li>Structural integrity issues</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">What's Not Covered:</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>Normal wear and tear</li>
            <li>Damage caused by improper care or accidents</li>
            <li>Loss or theft</li>
            <li>Alterations or repairs performed by unauthorized parties</li>
            <li>Natural characteristics of gemstones (inclusions, color variations)</li>
            <li>Damage from exposure to chemicals, extreme temperatures, or harsh environments</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Custom Jewelry Warranty</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Custom-designed jewelry pieces come with specific warranty terms that will be discussed and documented during the design process. Generally, custom pieces carry the same one-year warranty against manufacturing defects.</p>

        <p class="text-gray-700">Due to the unique nature of custom pieces, certain aspects may have different warranty considerations. These will be clearly communicated before your purchase is finalized.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Extended Warranty</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">For added peace of mind, we offer an optional extended warranty program that provides coverage for up to three years from the date of purchase. The extended warranty includes:</p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4 space-y-1">
            <li>All benefits of the standard warranty for an extended period</li>
            <li>One free professional cleaning per year</li>
            <li>One free ring sizing adjustment (if applicable)</li>
            <li>Priority repair service</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-700">Extended warranty options are available for purchase within 30 days of your original purchase. Please inquire in-store or contact our customer service for pricing and details.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Making a Warranty Claim</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">If you believe your jewelry has a defect covered by our warranty, please follow these steps:</p>

        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Contact our customer service team at Ottawa_Opal_Shop@hotmail.com or call +1 (613) 555-7890 to report the issue.</li>
            <li>Provide your proof of purchase and a detailed description of the problem, including photos if possible.</li>
            <li>Our team will evaluate your claim and provide instructions for returning the item if necessary.</li>
            <li>Once we receive and inspect the item, we will determine if the issue is covered under warranty.</li>
            <li>If covered, we will repair or replace the item at no cost to you.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>
